WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:32.950 --> 00:00:40.330
In the infinite, dark, and silent universe,
there is one place situated on planet Earth

00:00:40.330 --> 00:00:45.090
that is known as the belly of the world.

00:00:45.090 --> 00:00:47.020
It is the Czech Republic.

00:00:47.020 --> 00:00:54.530
The home of the Czechs,
who hold the world record for drinking beer.

00:00:54.530 --> 00:03:12.420
And you can see why Czechs say
that beer builds beautiful bodies.

